extends layout

block header
  h1 Plan

block content
  p You have no training plan. Get a plan for workout recommendations and
    | reminders.
  a(href="pick-plan.html", data-role="button", data-theme="b") Get a training plan

  h3 Or go exercise right now
  ul(data-role="listview")
    li(data-role="list-divider") Workouts You Can Do Now
    li: a(href="go.html") 20 Minute Walk
    li: a(href="go.html") 30 Minute Jog
    li: a(href="go.html") 1 Hour Tempo Run
    li: a(href="go.html")
      h3 Asana Yoga
      p $20. Starts at 3pm (in 30 minutes). 10 miles away.
    li: a(href="go.html")
      h3 Divis Up or Shut Up (Hill Run)
      p Free. Starts at 6:30pm (in 3:30 minutes). 10 miles away.

block footer
  mixin footer("plan")
